Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——————EP01部分——————
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,打算背著逃晚的人逃離 可是1樓已成火海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.51,0:00:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那之後呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.51,0:00:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就沿著2樓窗戶的窗檐逃脫出來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}真不愧是消防員 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.48,0:00:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,談得火熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}可是那是縱火事件 還沒抓到犯人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.23,0:00:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,藤橋小姐 在暍酒?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,涼 杯子都見底了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,店員小姐 梅酒沙瓦續杯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 颯馬你怎麼就擅自做主了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.87,0:00:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,呀 我一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,涼你公司的女孩 等級都很高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那你找個人交往不就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,聯誼都搞過幾次了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.71,0:00:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都是美人我很頭疼呢 之類的?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你到頭來就是想玩玩而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.35,0:00:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真是 很輕浮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.10,0:01:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1392,910)\fad(200,450)\fs58}第一話『今晚、要來…我家嗎?』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,現在幾點?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.78,0:01:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,話說這是什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.74,0:01:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,外面好亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.74,0:01:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧 火災?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不好 要避難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,救命啊 來人 救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.41,0:01:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託 來人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.42,0:01:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就算這樣做外面也不可能聽得見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.30,0:01:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可是光在這裡等 遲早也…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.84,0:01:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,涼! 涼!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.89,0:01:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事了 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.69,0:01:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 完全沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 颯馬?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.16,0:01:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不是活蹦亂跳嗎? 為什麼放棄求救了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.29,0:01:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,原來你聽見了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:01:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這可是性命攸關的關頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能聽漏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.17,0:02:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,還以為你已經失去意識 以為趕不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 沒事實在是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 錢包手機都沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,也不知道朋友們的聯繫方式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我這傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要來…我家嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.11,0:02:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 雖說是緊急情況就過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來…了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這怎麼搞的?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,別進這個範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不會進你的範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你讓我留宿我是很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可我也沒蠢到不戒備你這樣的花花公子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:02:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這點程度算不上什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,貼些藥布就能馬上康復
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可那裡你很難貼 要我幫你貼麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不是說不會踏入這邊麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了 你自己弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜 抓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怎 為什麼會變成這樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因為 我是花花公子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這算什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你說的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 你摸哪裡呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啊混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,明明一直在撩我 卻還敢過來的你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,被這個花花公子隨意擺弄的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,明明絕對會後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,背後傳來颯馬的熱度 我的身體也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你很敏感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊也想舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,很濕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:03:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能就這麼結束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你一個人舒服也太不公平了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我不插進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,明明沒插進來 卻很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你這樣的聲音我還是第一次聽見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺起來的涼 超級可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,被花花公子這樣說 也不覺得開心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是 不知道颯馬會是這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,涼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(586,670)\fad(250,300)\fs75}明明只是在淋浴…卻很舒服?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,愛的火焰是誰都澆不滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——————EP02部分——————
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 因為還有很多手續要辦 今天就去不了公司…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是的 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,涼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你拜託的東西我買來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不過你別過來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好心幫你買來東西 可不能這麼說我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你不要嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你的手機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1316,910)\fad(200,450)\fs58}第二話『明明只是在淋浴…卻很舒服?』
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這下就搞定身份證明了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 搞定手續了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你要跟著我到什麼時候?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 我的知識不是起作用了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就算如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我休息閒得很
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 下一個地方就是銀行囉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,居然請我吃這麼好吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:07:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,跟過來太正確了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,過於大驚小怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,能換上手機真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你新的手機畫面很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}也要重新登錄下我的手機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然他靠的很近也是平常事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,借用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,登錄一下我的聯絡方式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哈? 你擅自做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好 完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這下子聯誼的時間表能隨時掌握了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,開玩笑的 開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什麼麻煩 就聯絡我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,誰會找你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧 這雨怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,突然下這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 文件基本沒濕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,借你浴室 進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.42,0:08:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,一時間還有點不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,還好沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,呀 這雨真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你怎麼進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋 出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我的開關 開了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,只是幫你沖身子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來 你好像不擅長淋浴?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,明明以前那麼害怕 很舒服?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.59,0:09:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,都是以前的事 和現在沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,水 頂到敏感的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,已經站不住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:09:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你的表情很淫蕩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,誠實點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,水和手指同時…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,已經
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,要被牽著走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,明明不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,涼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬的溫度很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,涼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我要進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,涼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,只是這樣是滿足不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,被這樣弄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.63,0:11:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我會讓你爽上天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怎? 怎麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,停電了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,很危險 別亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這怎麼同事?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,聽到颯馬的呼吸和心跳聲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,比剛才還要近得多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,看來恢復要等很長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找能點亮的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好好待著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我 被牽著走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是停電 會就那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,藤橋小姐 你沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 這才是平常的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只是因為火災顯得軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,而依靠颯馬而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的中午 有消防演練哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,消防演練?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(725,670)\fad(250,300)\fs75}直到你說出隱瞞的話為止、都不住手。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,愛的火焰是誰都澆不滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——————EP03部分——————
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,身體伏低 慢慢移動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,到了外面就請在安全地區避難
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊進行滅火演練
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1210,910)\fad(200,450)\fs58}第三話『直到你說出隱瞞的話為止、都不住手。』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬他搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,完全沒聽說過他會過來公司啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,藤橋小姐 輪到我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不能直視啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭 真的很抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 請別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,太難為情了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我去給你換身衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我說涼你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我說你轉過去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你那有衣架嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,來 給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好遠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可你能夠到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是有點不留情面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,尺寸還可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不是讓你轉過去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣說過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來我自己來就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 為什麼要躲著我?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,沒為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.55,0:15:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,理由給我說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,因為太在意颯馬…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這怎麼可能說得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,等下 住手 這裡可是公司裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,才不住手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,居然瞞著我 超級傷心吶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你不也是 隱瞞了今天會過來公司這事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟你沒問啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼要躲著我?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,才沒躲你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎? 那直到你說出來之前我不會住手的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,慢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,身體開始變熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,比往常還要有感覺嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這怎麼…可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,藤橋小姐 剛才真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有需要我幫忙的地方嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,慢著 現在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事 只是滑了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,藤橋小姐 你真的沒事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.54,0:16:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事 話說下一次會議的準備就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我知道了 我這就去印刷資料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了 別發現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,幸好沒暴露啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真的住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,直到你說出隱瞞的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可以?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,說不出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.83,0:16:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,涼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣停下的話我很難受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:17:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不管 你自己擼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.05,0:17:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,對這樣的傢伙居然動了下心我也是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我再不理他了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我說你們啊 下一個休息日有空嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.31,0:17:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你要做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,邀請女生們 去煙火大會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.69,0:17:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,水野你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 他和他的青梅竹馬吵架中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,微信全是未讀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哈? 居然還沒拿下?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,再這樣磨磨蹭蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我就搶先一步拿下了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,水野 這可糟糕了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 讓她也去煙火大會不就好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會助你一臂之力的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,泉 這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,誒 今天是聯誼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不算聯誼 只是一起玩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,額 等一…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是很期待今天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,被丟下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,涼 那時候真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,明明錯在我身上 這麼說可能有些自私
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想和你這樣鬧彆扭下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,祭典 要不要一起逛?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,和颯馬逛祭典?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(840,750)\fad(250,300)\fs75}讓我看見這麼誘人的浴衣、怎麼可能忍得住。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,愛的火焰是誰都澆不滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——————EP04部分——————
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,和颯馬逛祭典?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,作為賠禮 今天全由我買單
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,全部?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 噢 全部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 我也很喜歡祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.00,0:20:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那首先我想去個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.07,0:20:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1135,866)\fad(200,450)\fs58}第四話『讓我看見這麼誘人的浴衣、怎麼可能忍得住。』
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真是各式各樣的都有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我要玩那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.01,0:20:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,射擊遊戲? 你要哪個?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼能打中啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就像在看中學生的戀愛似的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}沒錯 伸直胳膊 好好瞄準
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.94,0:20:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,藤橋小姐也會這樣玩鬧的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.85,0:20:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}所以說啊 是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 肯定不會一直這麼遷就她的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}可惡 你看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,秘傳香料或者激辣醬汁…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:20:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,全都要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:20:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 那個人是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,羽瀨先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 水野
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 朋友說來了這附近我才來這的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,可他說的店關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這家店上個月就搬遷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.43,0:21:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,應該不是很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我給他帶下路 你把那個買下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.94,0:21:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡嗎? 謝謝你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼再見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 藤橋小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,和水野在交往嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.61,0:21:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,才 才沒有在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,和颯馬只是青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.99,0:21:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 那麼不如和我交往?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,既然沒在交往 不如選我?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 我開不起這樣的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.09,0:21:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.21,0:21:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 颯馬在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:21:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 歡迎冋來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.81,0:22:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我說啊 涼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.86,0:22:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能轉過去一下?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.57,0:22:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,別問別問
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.99,0:22:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.95,0:22:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,誒 你什麼時候買的?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.07,0:22:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,買完章魚燒後還有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.12,0:22:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 你看 戴上這個後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.08,0:22:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,髮髻帶起的髮型很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這個確實很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,即將開始放煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.38,0:22:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}重複一遍 即將開始放煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.38,0:22:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 已經快要開始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.51,0:22:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要趕快去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.80,0:22:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,涼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不能 走散啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.48,0:22:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,注意腳邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.23,0:22:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,走這邊真的可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.02,0:22:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,呼哇 還有這種地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.19,0:22:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這種秘密地方 真是令人興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:22:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才讓你給羽瀨先生帶路真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你還是很歷害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.20,0:23:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那種時候還能馬上行動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.12,0:23:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,早在以前你就是做什麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.37,0:23:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼 也不是做什麼都行的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.58,0:23:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 你一直很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.46,0:23:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才覺得你這點很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.05,0:23:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,開 開玩笑的話倒是說得搞笑點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.06,0:23:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是開玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你很美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.15,0:23:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.45,0:23:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,慢著 我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.16,0:23:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘了來這祭典的原因了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.83,0:23:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看見這麼誘人的涼 才忍不住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.71,0:23:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就在這野外
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.60,0:24:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要是有人過來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.52,0:24:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定都在看煙火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.48,0:24:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,和房間做的時候不同
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.90,0:24:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.90,0:24:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,要是…弄髒浴衣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.03,0:24:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就好好張開你的大腿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.49,0:24:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,而且這邊好像期待得很
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.12,0:24:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.87,0:24:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,看我讓你洪水泛濫
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.38,0:26:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(775,630)\fad(250,300)\fs75}居然要我隱忍住、其他男人向你搭訕…。
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.24,0:26:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,愛的火焰是誰都澆不滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——————EP05部分——————
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.63,0:26:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.22,0:26:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,抓緊囉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.47,0:26:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.84,0:26:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,涼你那裡 我明明還沒插進來卻吸得我好緊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.72,0:26:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡這姿勢?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.90,0:27:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.53,0:27:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 颯馬那裡的溫度 讓我腦袋一片空自
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.34,0:27:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這聲音很好 幸好沒被煙火聲蓋住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.47,0:27:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.68,0:27:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,要去 要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.72,0:27:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可別自己一個人去了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.46,0:28:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,涼 你很適合浴衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.92,0:28:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這話說得也太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.00,0:28:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.35,0:28:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.02,0:28:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這都是拜誰所賜
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.77,0:28:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧是我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.48,0:28:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要我背你?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.40,0:28:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,免了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.69,0:28:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是一片好心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.36,0:28:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我並不討厭被這樣牽著走
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.61,0:28:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我這是 喜歡颯馬他嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.20,0:28:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.78,0:28:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 要不要一起去?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.54,0:28:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我們兩個去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.71,0:28:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是大家一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.00,0:28:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(880,730)\fad(200,450)\fs68\c&H608396&\1a&H20&\3c&H282828&\3a&HFF&}第五話『居然要我隱忍住、其他男人向你搭訕…。』
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.18,0:28:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.34,0:28:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.56,0:29:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.98,0:29:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.94,0:29:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,要小心點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.94,0:29:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才那小哥好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.77,0:29:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的菜誒
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.61,0:29:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那組人不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.32,0:29:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,哦? 那我們上嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.03,0:29:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我們今天不是還帶著女生嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.78,0:29:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.79,0:29:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,藤橋小姐 那邊有空位
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.12,0:29:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,趕快撐起遮陽傘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.00,0:29:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.38,0:29:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.17,0:29:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,放下行李後 來玩這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.05,0:29:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.09,0:29:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不太擅長球類運動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.26,0:29:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係沒關係 會按男女分成一組的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.18,0:29:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我們這就去弄好抽籤
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.43,0:29:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你們懂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.39,0:29:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這次的沙灘排球
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.77,0:29:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,拿到第一的人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.77,0:29:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,能獲得跟女孩子搭訕的權利
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.23,0:29:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.82,0:29:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是要這樣才更好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.32,0:29:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不過這點人來說 也就是玩玩的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.32,0:30:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,果然變成這樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.82,0:30:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼抽籤的結果 第一回合
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.45,0:30:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,羽瀨藤橋組合對水野筱田組合
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.00,0:30:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,墊底的組合可是要在燒烤過後負責收拾妥當
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.50,0:30:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.55,0:30:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,羽瀨君 你可要手下留情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.96,0:30:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.13,0:30:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,和涼分在不同的隊伍嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.47,0:30:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,泉和羽瀨應該都不會盯上涼的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.47,0:30:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可還是不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.02,0:30:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,比賽 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.27,0:30:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 總之只能贏下就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.53,0:30:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好 這樣的話還…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.53,0:30:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,羽瀨先生 傳給我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.33,0:30:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就算羽瀨先生放水 我也會認真對待的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.33,0:30:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,收拾 絕對要避兔
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.00,0:30:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不 涼 你不能贏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.09,0:30:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,藤橋小姐你有打過球?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.38,0:31:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是在高中的球技大賽打過
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.72,0:31:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我說羽瀨先生 你這不是被女生搶光風頭了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.64,0:31:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯也是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.56,0:31:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也拿出真正實力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.80,0:32:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(670,740)\fad(250,300)\fs75}晚上的游泳池、沒人會來……吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.49,0:32:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,愛的火焰是誰都澆不滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——————EP06部分——————
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.00,0:33:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,勝方 羽瀨藤橋組合
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.34,0:33:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,下面就是和我們打了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.26,0:33:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,還真不想輸給你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.93,0:33:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,羽瀨先生和小涼 進展不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.21,0:33:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}謝謝你的輔助
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.81,0:33:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,到頭來排墊底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.40,0:33:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}這都是泉君你的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.48,0:33:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子餓了嗎 我去買些吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.69,0:33:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,給大家都買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.07,0:33:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那我也幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.40,0:33:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.80,0:33:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1268,910)\fad(200,450)\fs58}第六話『晚上的游泳池、沒人會來……吧?』
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.87,0:33:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.25,0:33:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.50,0:33:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,烤肉 最棒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.30,0:33:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,泉君 你剛才就只吃肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.84,0:33:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我去拿些飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.80,0:33:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.06,0:33:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,沒被燒傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.06,0:33:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.10,0:33:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.10,0:34:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這個已經可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.77,0:34:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,還要烤久點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.11,0:34:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,泉 你這是要全都放嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.44,0:34:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,當然 搞一次大的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.53,0:34:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真拿他沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.49,0:34:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 不如我拿一個?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.50,0:34:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.33,0:34:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真不愧是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.00,0:34:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 還是能幫我拿一下嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.13,0:34:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.67,0:34:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得你是那種手閒不下來的那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.09,0:34:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可能你說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.68,0:34:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,祭典的時候 謝謝你特意給我帶路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.81,0:34:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.23,0:34:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊 覺得藤橋小姐你這點真的很吸引我
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.24,0:34:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,額 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.66,0:34:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能我和交往?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.57,0:34:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你和水野只是一般的青梅竹馬而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.00,0:35:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,涼她是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.42,0:35:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,把這個
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.88,0:35:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,搬走就可以了?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.68,0:35:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 涼? 為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.30,0:35:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,覺得你一個人很辛苫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.39,0:35:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,筱田小姐呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.85,0:35:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,只剩下搬這個就可以 就讓她先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.10,0:35:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.06,0:35:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我說 羽瀨先生呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.40,0:35:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他在放煙花那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.45,0:35:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,也 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.66,0:35:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,也不知道他說的是真是假
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.20,0:35:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是不擅長應付他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.25,0:35:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.12,0:35:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.55,0:35:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.80,0:35:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.68,0:35:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這個游泳池 我們可以用嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.85,0:36:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,泉他說可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.85,0:36:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那就去游一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.02,0:36:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,冷冰冰的好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.78,0:36:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊 居然還帶有游泳池…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.90,0:36:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.91,0:36:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.41,0:36:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,誰都不會過來 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.04,0:36:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,颯 馬
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.27,0:36:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭 已經洪水泛濫 太羞恥了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.53,0:36:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,涼
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.32,0:36:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬那厚實的手掌
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.87,0:37:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬那熱情的體溫
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.21,0:37:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.79,0:37:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬那溫情的細語
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.25,0:37:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.34,0:37:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我 忍到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.61,0:38:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(440,810)\fad(250,300)\fs75}絕對會救你的。
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.11,0:38:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,愛的火焰是誰都澆不滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——————EP07部分——————
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.70,0:39:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我絕對 不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.00,0:39:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一次又一次地和他做
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.46,0:39:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.13,0:39:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,涼
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.63,0:39:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,本該只是一般的青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.89,0:39:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,涼
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.32,0:39:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,涼
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.19,0:39:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 快點進來
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.45,0:40:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,對我來說 颯馬是
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.17,0:40:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.02,0:40:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.52,0:40:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎麼看我的?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.57,0:40:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼看? 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.61,0:40:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,一般的青梅竹馬嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.49,0:40:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是的話
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.16,0:40:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,涼 你是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.04,0:40:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.00,0:41:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1460,910)\fad(200,450)\fs58}第七話『絕對會救你的。』
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.30,0:41:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.51,0:41:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,下個休息日 要不要一起出去?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.97,0:41:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就我們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.10,0:41:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我去看看日程表再通知你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.11,0:41:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我也會找個休假的日子通知你的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.36,0:41:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.49,0:41:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(940,420)\fs40\frz20\frx12\3c&H282828&\3a&HFF&\c&H000000&}下個星期六怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.49,0:41:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1100,545)\fs40\frz20\frx12\3c&H282828&\3a&HFF&\c&H000000&}嗯 那天沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.65,0:41:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.04,0:41:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是 縱火犯
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.21,0:41:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,必須報警
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.42,0:41:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.67,0:41:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.59,0:41:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.55,0:41:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才 工廠區前有個縱火犯…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.31,0:41:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你 看見了?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.14,0:41:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,涼 怎麼了? 涼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.02,0:41:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.65,0:41:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,該死 逃得真快
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.32,0:42:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.57,0:42:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.83,0:42:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 讓我費盡功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.63,0:42:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,颯 馬
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.96,0:42:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,涼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.26,0:42:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.22,0:42:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,水野 就這樣抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.14,0:42:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,給我過來 老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.39,0:42:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,涼 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.10,0:42:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 沒事 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.31,0:42:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,三號街發生火災 請求出動
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.40,0:42:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.66,0:42:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,工廠內發生火災 裡面可能有數名工人被困在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.50,0:43:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這可難搞了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.09,0:43:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,分頭去找
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.18,0:43:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,發現一名被困人員
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.01,0:43:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,配合動作 起
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.35,0:43:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一 二 三 起
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.89,0:43:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.10,0:43:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,還有一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.11,0:43:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,還有一個人 在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.78,0:43:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,趕快將這名先生帶去安全地區
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.33,0:43:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,發現一名被困人員
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.74,0:43:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,營救被困人員
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.12,0:43:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,趕緊撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.72,0:45:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(500,600)\fad(250,300)\fs75}現在只需要看著我。
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.22,0:45:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,愛的火焰是誰都澆不滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——————EP08部分——————
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.20,0:45:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.50,0:45:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.79,0:45:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 工作結束後明天就去聯誼
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.63,0:45:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,會有可愛的女孩子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.67,0:45:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,只要是女孩子我是來著不拒的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.95,0:45:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1436,910)\fad(200,450)\fs58}第八話『現在只需要看著我』
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.68,0:45:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.06,0:45:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 仔細想想就不該打給颯馬 而是報警吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.27,0:46:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧你聯絡我 才能將受害程度最小限度地抑制下去
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.07,0:46:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你受傷了吧 腳疼不疼?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.20,0:46:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,沒 沒事 畢竟已經去看過…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.79,0:46:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很疼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.87,0:46:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是的 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.96,0:46:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,還是說
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.21,0:46:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,來感覺了?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.38,0:46:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那個地方 太髒了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.84,0:46:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,平常那麼強硬的涼 向我求饒的樣子太誘惑人了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.81,0:46:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是個輕浮的男人 為什麼會有這樣的眼神?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.43,0:46:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因為這個 我才對颯馬他…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.86,0:46:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這份感情 如果這只屬於我的話有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.69,0:46:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.03,0:46:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.49,0:46:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,涼?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.74,0:46:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 為什麼這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.00,0:46:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,明明知道你再怎麼溫柔 你也是個誰都可以的人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.75,0:47:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那為什麼還會因為你而有這種心情
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.42,0:47:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 你在較真什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.88,0:47:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我和輕浮的你不同
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.30,0:47:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,想找炮友的話請左轉
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.19,0:47:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 涼
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.74,0:47:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是誰都可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.53,0:47:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,只有涼你啊 我想在一起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.53,0:47:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就是想和你在一起 對我來說你在我身邊是那麼的理所當然
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.58,0:47:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不然的話我可不願意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.75,0:47:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡你 涼
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.17,0:47:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.92,0:47:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.67,0:47:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.55,0:47:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.80,0:47:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你現在這麼說我也無法相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.64,0:47:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,涼 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.27,0:48:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你說得也太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.40,0:48:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,淨耍帥 輕浮男就該有輕浮男的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.49,0:48:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你還真是不坦率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.70,0:48:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 別再胡思亂想了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.20,0:48:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,現在只需要看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.62,0:48:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我也只會看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.63,0:48:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬那裡 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.05,0:48:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,插到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.80,0:48:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.64,0:48:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,別擋著臉
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.47,0:48:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,總覺得 好羞人
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.39,0:48:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,都事到如今了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.68,0:48:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因 因為 和颯馬這麼
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.14,0:48:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼還能變大啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.48,0:48:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,還不是你 說些可愛的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.44,0:48:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所以別再說了啊 太羞人了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.03,0:48:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你還真是
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.78,0:48:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.57,0:48:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在我看來 這全都很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.95,0:48:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,涼 我喜歡你 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.04,0:49:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真是 說得也太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.46,0:49:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是 喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.30,0:49:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬 你再慢點
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.68,0:49:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能 停不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.56,0:49:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.77,0:49:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.73,0:49:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.10,0:49:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.53,0:49:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 好深
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.53,0:49:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬 我已經
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.45,0:49:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,光是插進來我就快去了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.20,0:49:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊 我還沒射呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.25,0:49:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧 等 慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.04,0:49:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,停下 我要瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.42,0:49:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不會停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.40,0:50:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,颯馬 讓你久等 等的很久了?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.99,0:50:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.49,0:50:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,都是鄰居一起出發不好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.53,0:50:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這你不懂 等女孩子可是約會的樂趣之一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.58,0:50:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.37,0:50:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 今天的店是個好地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.34,0:50:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 嘛 那當然…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.00,0:50:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.01,0:50:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯啊 我是打算好好表白做了好多準備…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.05,0:50:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 真是的 遜斃了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.51,0:50:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很遺憾?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.77,0:50:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.89,0:50:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是能和女朋友一起去更好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.65,0:50:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎?
